Title: 26inch Majestic Headboard Strutted Headboard
Body (HTML):
In this section, we have selected a range of our best popular headboards which we believe offer exceptional value for money, are beautifully made with care and available in-store in a fantastic choice of over 40 fabrics and colors.

Thesingle headboard grey are made in either the traditional way, with single bed headboards, or as a floor standing model which is still attached to the divan base.

The headboards are available in the standard 6 sizes :

2ft6 (75cm) Small Single : 3ft0 (90cm) Single : 4ft0 (120cm) Small Double : 4ft6 (135cm) Double : 5ft0 (150cm) King and 6ft0 (180cm) SuperKing :

Other special sizes are available in this range, please telephone us for a quote.

To show some of the fabric colors , single divan headboard, as a guide and of course these could be ordered online should you wish to do so.
